@startuml
title Two hypotheses, two corrections

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundCorner 10
skinparam defaultFontName Helvetica
skinparam defaultFontColor #111827
skinparam ArrowColor #4B5563
skinparam ArrowFontColor #374151
skinparam rectangle {
  BorderColor #4B5563
  FontColor #111827
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
}

rectangle "Hypothesis 1\nRemove the (N, V) logits matrix\nto train longer contexts" as h1 #DBEAFE
rectangle "8,192-token training result\nFused and stock marginal peaks tie\nat 21.39 GiB" as tie #FECACA
rectangle "Isolated attention probe\nForward-plus-backward reaches 12.75 GiB\nand grows about 3.7-3.8x per doubling" as probe #FEF3C7
rectangle "Implementation response\nTiled FlashAttention forward and backward\nSaved attention state scales with N x D" as flash #DCFCE7
rectangle "Hypothesis 2\nThe projected duration of the whole\npacked launch chain is the kill unit" as h2 #DBEAFE
rectangle "MLX source and packing probe\nLarge production ranges each trigger\na command-buffer commit" as packing #FECACA
rectangle "Guard correction\nBudget each command buffer separately\nKeep the safety margin unchanged" as guard #DCFCE7
rectangle "Source-reported later sweep\n23,040 tokens on flash + fused\n7,936 tokens on the stock path" as sweep #EDE9FE

h1 -down-> tie : measured
tie -down-> probe : investigate shared peak
probe -down-> flash : change the bottleneck
flash -right-> h2 : exposes a new limit
h2 -down-> packing : inspect submission behavior
packing -down-> guard : correct the model
guard -down-> sweep : measure after correction

caption Conceptual evidence sequence. Values are source-reported; this is not an allocation-lifetime trace.
@enduml
